copo-tracer
===========

This is a small test environment to render scenes with a
ray-tracer. It is meant to elaborate some different snow
rendering techniques. There are no further dependencies.
The original source code was provided by Sören König
(Soeren.Koenig AT tu-dresden.de). You are free to modify
and/or redistribute that code in terms of the BSD license.


Building
========

The project uses cmake and recommends an out-of-source build,
e.g. for a Linux system:

    mkdir build
    cd build
    cmake ..
    make

